Q21.Remove div section elements after clicking on button using jQuery. [Hint: Use #id selector] 

Answer:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
<html>
<head>
<script src="jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
	<script>
		$(document).ready(function()
		{
			$("#b1").click(function()
			{
				$("#d").remove();
			});
		});
	</script>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="d">Hello</div>
	<button id="b1" type="submit">Remove</button>
</body>
</html>
